1. Create Receipes Folder
2. Open that folder in VS code and in terminal enter this
   npm create vite@latest . -- --template react
   and install it
   ➜ Local: http://localhost:5173/ choose this option
   Then run this
   npm install react-router-dom tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite
   Then open open vite.config.js this file

Replace everything inside with this
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'
import tailwindcss from '@tailwindcss/vite'

export default defineConfig({
plugins: [react(), tailwindcss()],
})

Then Open src/index.css

Delete everything and put:

@import "tailwindcss";

Every time you work on the project

Open the terminal inside your project folder:

cd Receipes
npm run dev

You'll see something like:

VITE v8.x.x ready

Local:
http://localhost:5173/

Open:

http://localhost:5173/

That's your app.

